Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:42.09,screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\fnDotted Songti Square\c&HCACACA&\3c&HCACACA&\bord0.6\blur3\pos(960,883)\clip(1172,0,1172,1080)\t(0,720,\clip(961,0,1172,1080))}我們是 Dragon Keeper!
